oad%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F223651_f97cf28e7e05dbdc98fd2ab20dc7a5f5.jpg&h=af62303f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好郁下就唔要個結他，好浪費</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整得好一定整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755be4ace541140971f5189e04d5961440bb6d1d","tid":42251,"uid":66494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可能頸彎咗 呢啲少問題啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下呢枝野你對佢有無感情或者睇價錢<br />\n係就拎去俾人整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIbanez v50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係陪我過左兩年宿舍生活加上自己又唔係好勁所以唔想換</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎去俾人整囉 自己整唔識整到時都係要拎去俾人整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8aea6681a592d6bce8d138132895438f768c36","tid":42251,"uid":39889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:48:22.000Z","msg":"冇經驗自己磨fret<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你好運"},{"pid":"2c575494786e2d520650270c5779a13eb066fa1b","tid":42251,"uid":39084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能頸彎咗 呢啲少問題啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下呢枝野你對佢有無感情或者睇價錢<br />\n係就拎去俾人整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIbanez v50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係陪我過左兩年宿舍生活加上自己又唔係好勁所以唔想換</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎去俾人整囉 自己整唔識整到時都係要拎去俾人整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就要睇下支野貴唔貴，唔係好貴可以一試. 磨得唔好最多咪換一兩條fret. 我地整結他嘅會用圖左邊嘅工具做leveling, 你冇工具就用右邊嘅木條再用雙面膠紙痴砂紙去磨，不過要確保條木係平. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U29C9Ds.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU29C9Ds.jpg&h=625e57bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以用#1000/#1200砂紙慢慢磨，千其唔好急，因為聽你講應該只係少少唔平.<br />\n<br />\n你只要用好簡單嘅工具就可以檢查到邊度唔平. 一陣再話你知，而家有野做."},{"pid":"8802196ed61ad5f1eac9f4b13357c719a30a80fe","tid":42251,"uid":39084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"首先用條可以橫跨3條fret嘅圓柱體，放係3條fret上面，用手指放係兩端好搖搖板咁搖，如果唔平就會郁，你就會知邊度高或低左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WR98Lf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WR98Lf.jpg&h=bd9e2f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住用小圓銼係條木條銼條溝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68o4vC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68o4vC8.jpg&h=d3c5ccaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/234115_21c04cbd3799719a84dd1935a0024049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F234115_21c04cbd3799719a84dd1935a0024049.jpg&h=d4ab9d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將砂紙如圖咁放去磨高左嘅地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/234324_6de569854ddfc51e3398939fccd42346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F234324_6de569854ddfc51e3398939fccd42346.jpg&h=5d9c56bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/234325_0e6f13543b860c4d24b5238965802098.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F234325_0e6f13543b860c4d24b5238965802098.jpg&h=7c0d6117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你想磨快d就用#400砂紙，驚就用高d如#1000，記得痴保護膠紙係琴頸.<br />\n完左用#1500，#2000砂紙打磨一下. 呢個方應該唔難，不過試唔試就睇你自己啦."},{"pid":"21bc7df34a1fba97114d796ae7f8fe0a307e1c80","tid":42251,"uid":42215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先用條可以橫跨3條fret嘅圓柱體，放係3條fret上面，用手指放係兩端好搖搖板咁搖，如果唔平就會郁，你就會知邊度高或低左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WR98Lf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WR98Lf.jpg&h=bd9e2f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住用小圓銼係條木條銼條溝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68o4vC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68o4vC8.jpg&h=d3c5ccaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/234115_21c04cbd3799719a84dd1935a0024049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F234115_21c04cbd3799719a84dd1935a0024049.jpg&h=d4ab9d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將砂紙如圖咁放去磨高左嘅地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/234324_6de569854ddfc51e3398939fccd42346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F234324_6de569854ddfc51e3398939fccd42346.jpg&h=5d9c56bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/234325_0e6f13543b860c4d24b5238965802098.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F234325_0e6f13543b860c4d24b5238965802098.jpg&h=7c0d6117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你想磨快d就用#400砂紙，驚就用高d如#1000，記得痴保護膠紙係琴頸.<br />\n完左用#1500，#2000砂紙打磨一下. 呢個方應該唔難，不過試唔試就睇你自己啦.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}